Titolo: Real Sound: Kaze no Regret

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Real Sound: Kaze no Regret, literally "Real Sound: Wind of Regret", is an adventure audio game developed by Warp and published by Sega. The game was first released for the Saturn in July 1997, and later for the Dreamcast in March 1999. Real Sound was intended to provide equal access to sighted and blind players. The subtitle Kaze no Regret means "wind of regret".